{"tid":1712072,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"成世人都着緊唔會對我好嘅人","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T17:04:38.000Z","uid":188621,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3170e757bec96aca15686d1ee62c631a0d255723","tid":1712072,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:20:05.000Z","msg":"傷，係感傷嗰種傷。<br />\n傷，係淡然嘅哀傷。<br />\n傷，係心up嘅悲傷。<br />\n<br />\n我的心真的受傷了。<br />\n<br />\n一個，兩個，三個，四個，五個，六個，七個。<br />\n<br />\n第一個，中學萬人迷，練band識嘅。<br />\n第二個，青梅竹馬，結果移咗民。<br />\n第三個，我由衷傾慕嘅。<br />\n第四個，我比唔上個官/富二代。<br />\n第五個，我以為係佢，但係原來喺佢心目中我咩都唔係，仲要突然一拍兩散。<br />\n第六個，我覺得佢嘅冷漠係理所當然嘅，我鐘意佢嗰種愛理不理嘅態度。<br />\n第七個，熱心到幫佢揾兩份好工。<br />\n<br />\n點解呢個世界我鐘意一個人，對佢好，最後唔會有回報。<br />\n<br />\n我唔稀罕施捨，我只要求有來有往。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe0fb4de85f1ff917ca3956eb5364159dd3e2401","tid":1712072,"uid":37959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"彈開啦 打緊仗仲叫春"},{"pid":"1756657676470935c11e771398ff84faef6e45e5","tid":1712072,"uid":70897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"5815755e018550cdd4354494a638892fbe7067ea","tid":1712072,"uid":188621,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"fe0fb4de85f1ff917ca3956eb5364159dd3e2401","tid":1712072,"uid":37959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:21:36.000Z","msg":"彈開啦 打緊仗仲叫春"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:23:12.000Z","msg":"個個喺感情台都叫得，得我唔叫得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00a17a75662d10e130d2e0e25d3704145c14ff9b","tid":1712072,"uid":282544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"你而家轉個台，就唔會再諗呢啲野"},{"pid":"86871d2de2ab4cb7f23debb18224b9a4d331964b","tid":1712072,"uid":188621,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"00a17a75662d10e130d2e0e25d3704145c14ff9b","tid":1712072,"uid":282544,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:28:59.000Z","msg":"你而家轉個台，就唔會再諗呢啲野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"第七個，個幾月以來一個whatsapp都無，一開聲就拜託我幫佢揾工，我又唔忍心唔幫手。今日見成咗個offer仲幾好，就問我近況如何。<br />\n<br />\n我幫到佢係開心但係我好難受。"},{"pid":"18982fa758fafd1f3bd518a95663f78183b376df","tid":1712072,"uid":224190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"處女？"},{"pid":"f9e63c8336ab42f8314796203d2b58e0b8ca4038","tid":1712072,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T17:04:38.000Z","msg":"著緊你嘅又俾你冷待嘅姐"}]}